txt.en: Dígelir, queen of the Great Spiders of Mirkwood, has established a nest in the heart of the Scuttledells, where she is breeding an army to answer the call of Sauron.
Complete the quest Webs of the Scuttledells -- Challenge
You must burn all the cocoons and webs within Dígelir's nest before defeating Dígelir herself.
